body:
Span has method like the following ,

``` java
 public static Span prefix(Bytes row, Bytes cf)
 public static Span prefix(Bytes row, Bytes cf, Bytes cq)
 public static Span prefix(Bytes row, Bytes cf, Bytes cq, Bytes cvPrefix)
```

Could these be replaced w/ the following w/ this change?

``` java
 public static Span prefix(Bytes row, Column col)
```

Yes.. It looks like we condense both exact and prefix from 8 methods each to 4:

``` java
public static Span exact(Bytes row)
public static Span exact(String row)
public static Span exact(Bytes row, Column col)
public static Span exact(String row, Column col)

public static Span prefix(Bytes row)
public static Span prefix(String row)
public static Span prefix(Bytes row, Column col)
public static Span prefix(String row, Column col)
```
